  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the air fryer to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Roll out the puff pastry and cut it into a large square.",
    "Transfer the puff pastry to a greased air fryer basket.",
    "Mix the dulce de leche, cinnamon, ginger, smoked paprika, and sugar (if using) in a bowl.",
    "Pour the dulce de leche mixture over the center of the puff pastry, leaving a 1-inch border.",
    "Fold the puff pastry over the filling, pressing the edges to seal.",
    "Brush the egg over the pastry and sprinkle with sugar (if using).",
    "Air fry for 12-15 minutes, or until the pastry is golden brown and the filling is bubbly.",
    "Let cool for 5 minutes before serving."
  ],
